OL,7,FColleagues of Dr Michael Mosley have
OL,8,Fled tributes, hailing the late TV
OL,9,Fbroadcaster, producer and columnist as
OL,10,Fa "national treasure" and a "kind and
OL,11,Fgentle man", after his death while
OL,12,Fholidaying on a Greek island was
OL,13,Fconfirmed.
OL,15,FThe 67-year-old TV personality was
OL,16,Fwith friends at Agios Nikolaos beach
OL,17,Fon Symi on Wednesday before going
OL,18,Fmissing during a walk by himself to
OL,19,Fthe centre of the island.
