OL,7,FClare Bailey Mosley confirmed a body
OL,8,Ffound on Sunday morning in a rocky
OL,9,Farea near Agia Marina beach on Symi
OL,10,Fwas her husband, describing the loss
OL,11,Fas "devastating".
OL,13,FMimi Spencer, who co-authored The Fast
OL,14,FDiet with Dr Mosley, paid tribute to
OL,15,Fhim as "immediately likeable,
OL,16,Fgenuinely funny" and said she will
OL,17,F"miss him terribly".
